Module it.polimi.ingsw.PSP034

Package it.polimi.ingsw.PSP034.view.GUI

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GUIController
    Interface implemented by each GUI controller.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChooseGodsController
    It controls the GUI scene of the divinity cards' choice by the god-like player.
    DialogController
    It controls the GUI dialogs, blocking all interaction but the click on the Ok button.
    FirstPlayerController
    It controls the GUI scene of the first player choice.
    GUIRequestHub
    Is a singleton that handles all the messages and information between the server and the GUI controllers.
    MainGUI
    Starting GUI class.
    NameColorController
    It controls the GUI scene of the user registration with a name and a color
    NumberOfPlayersController
    It controls the GUI scene of the number of players choice by the first connected player.
    PersonalGodController
    It controls the GUI scene of the personal god choice between the cards picked by the god like player.
    ScenePath
    It contains all the paths of the fxml files that create all the different scenes.
    ServerLoginController
    It controls the GUI scene of the connection to a server and to a port.
    TableController
    It controls the GUI scene of the board
    TitleController
    It controls the opening GUI scene of the title
    WaitingController
    It controls the GUI scene of the waiting moments during the registration and setup of all the players.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    GodPath
    It contains all the paths of the gods and the corresponding power.
